AddressInfo.Title: Winnemucca RV Park
AddressInfo.AccessComments: From Reno/I-80 - Take exit 178. Turn right. Get in left lane immediately. Turn left on East Winnemucca Blvd. Go 1 mile. Park is on the left side of the street.  From Salt Lake City - Take Exit 180. Turn left. Go 1.2 miles to park. 2nd RV park on the right.  From US 95 southbound - Turn left at 1st stoplight (West Winnemucca Blvd). Go 1/2 mile, then turn right on East Winnemucca Blvd. Go 1 mile to park, on the left side.

GeneralComments: http://www.winnemuccarvpark.com/   WIFI Access Open year round Clean showers and restrooms    Large heated pool (seasonal)   Camp store, laundry, propane, RV supplies Owner/operator lives on site Free casino shuttle and coupons
